content:
Assign Learning to Agents with Agent Engagement

No one wants to feel like just a number. Balancing your business’ productivity needs with your agents’ career growth goals creates a support environment where full-time agents want to stick around.

Agent engagement lets agents earn skills by taking enablement site (myTrailhead) modules. To assign learning modules to your agents:

Open Omni Supervisor.
Select the agents to whom you'd like to assign learning.
Click Assign Learning.
Search for and select the module.
Click Assign Learning.

Workforce Engagement is available in Lightning Experience, Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions. User permissions are required: Workforce Engagement Planner.
title: Agent Engagement in Service Cloud
